<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>الْمَنْسُوبُونَ إِلَى خِلَافِ الظَّاهِرِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٩٣٥ - وَنَسَبُوا <span style="color:#6c6c00">«الْبَدْرِيَّ»</span> وَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«الْخُوزِيَّا»</span> … لِكَوْنِهِ جَاوَرَ وَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«التَّيْمِيَّا»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٩٣٦ - كَذَلِكَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«الْحَذَّاءُ»</span> لِلْجَلَّاسِ … وَمِقْسَمٌ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مَوْلَى بَنِي عَبَّاسِ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
